name: Buitan Food and Coffee
address: Jl. Raya Manggis, Manggis, Kec. Manggis, Kabupaten Karangasem, Bali 80871, Indonesia
review 1:
Super friendly owners! Great coffee with generous portion.
View of the water.
Come for relaxing respite along your travels.
review 2: We stopped for lunch. Mei Goreng for lunch and Pisang Goreng for dessert. That and two bottles of water 40k. Good food. Good taste. Great value.
review 3:
Best location, friendly and clean.. Most importantly the food is delicious and at affordable price.

If you like to try some of Balinese cuisine, you can find it here. Try their signature sambal, Sambal Embe, it is so special as they are using shrimp paste from Lombok.. Very very delicious ðŸ˜Š
review 4: Good place for eat and beverage..

name: Warung Muslim Ibu Nur
address: jln raya candida buitan kampung buitan, Manggis, Kec. Manggis, Kabupaten Karangasem, Bali, Indonesia
review 1: This place is incredible! I have been buying Nasi Campur (mixed rice) for the past 14 years and it always delightful. Nothing fancy, just steamed rice, fish of chicken (depending on that she has cooked that morning) green vegetables, Tempe, Tofu and some sambal, if you like it hot. It comes either in a waxed paper cone or sometimes a banana leaf. Ibu Nur is usually sold out by 1300, so if you are looking for a quick lunch or later dinner, get there between 1100 and 1230! It refrigerates very well and heats up in a microwave in about 2 minutes!! Well worth the Rp 10,000.... It has been my nightly meal for all these many past years. Ibu Nur is a very pleasant woman and tolerates broken Bahasa Indonesia well....
